dc_title_s: Map showing Pierhead and Bulkhead Line on Easterly Shore of Little Egg Harbor at Beach Haven
dc_description_s: Sheet 1: Map shows the pierhead (Wharf Line) of grants and extension grants issued. Grants are marked with bearings and distance. Map shows former mhwl. Also shown are Parker Island and Mordecai Island. |Sheet 2: Map shows the pierhead (Wharf Line) of the grants and extension grants issued. Grants are marked with bearings and distance. Map shows former mhwl of grants in 1905.
